## Standard Build

```bash
cargo build --release
```

## Hardware Backends

Select your hardware backend via Cargo features:

| Backend | Feature Flag | Hardware |
|---------|--------------|----------|
| CPU     | (default)    | x86_64, ARM64 |
| CUDA    | `cuda`       | NVIDIA GPUs |
| Metal   | `metal`      | Apple Silicon |
| ROCm    | `rocm`       | AMD GPUs |

## Development

To run with full logging:
```bash
RUST_LOG=debug cargo run --bin server-backend
```

